{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017gmqeEKf6mhb7ddyR9LufE","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect, I have all the information now. Let me compile the comprehensive inventory:\n\n## Frontend User-Profile/Transaction-History Feature Inventory\n\n### 1. **Types Definition**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts`\n\n- **TransactionEvent type** (line 245): `type TransactionEvent = \"join\" | \"win\" | \"loss\" | \"refund\";`\n- **ProfileTransaction type** (lines 247-255):\n  ```typescript\n  export interface ProfileTransaction {\n    id: string;\n    gameId: GameId;\n    matchId: string;\n    event: TransactionEvent;\n    amountLamports: string;\n    txSig: string | null;\n    createdAt: string;\n  }\n  ```\n- **GameId type** (line 171): includes \"coinflip\", \"lord-of-rngs\", \"close-call\", plus others\n- **GAME_NAMES mapping** (lines 173-179): Maps gameId to display names (\"Flip You\", \"Jackpot\", \"Close Call\", etc.)\n\n---\n\n### 2. **useTransactions Hook**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts` (124 lines)\n\n**Key Details**:\n- **API endpoint** (line 71): `GET ${BACKEND_URL}/profile/transactions?${qs}`\n- **Auth header** (line 73): Bearer token from `getAccessToken()` (JWT)\n- **Cursor pagination** (lines 43, 60, 95): `nextCursor` state manages pagination\n- **Game filter** (line 61): Optional `game` query param when filtering by game ID\n- **Limit** (line 59): Hard-coded to `limit=20` per page\n- **State management**: tracks `transactions`, `loading`, `loadingMore`, `error`, `nextCursor`\n- **API Response type** (lines 26-29):\n  ```typescript\n  interface ApiResponse {\n    transactions: ApiTransaction[];\n    nextCursor: string | null;\n  }\n  ```\n- **Mapping** (lines 80-88): Maps API field `game` (string) → `gameId` (GameId type)\n- **Abort hand