{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012r4bHWdjpqbZ8wTpLbiUVJ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Now let me compile the complete inventory:\n\n## Test Inventory: User Profile / Transaction History Feature\n\n### 1. **Local E2E Test**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/20-profile-transactions.spec.ts`\n\n**Test**: `Profile transactions › shows transaction history after coinflip settlement` (line 37)\n- **Line Range**: 37–116\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Plays a complete coinflip match (create → join → settlement)\n  - Navigates to `/profile` after settlement\n  - Clicks the \"Transactions\" tab\n  - Verifies transaction table appears with exactly 2 rows (join + win/loss outcome)\n  - Verifies game name maps correctly (\"coinflip\" → \"Flip You\")\n  - Verifies event types (JOIN and WIN/LOSS present)\n  - Verifies amounts display in SOL\n  - Verifies transaction rows contain match deep-links to `/coinflip/:matchId` format\n  - Tracks console errors for no unexpected messages\n  - Uses fixtures (playerAPage, playerBPage) with serial execution mode\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Visual Snapshot Tests**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`\n\n#### Test 1: `State variants › Profile page › wallet connected` (line 51)\n- **Line Range**: 51–88\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Navigates to `/profile` with wallet disconnected\n  - Connects wallet via UI\n  - Captures full-page screenshot: `profile-connected.png`\n  - Uses `maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.03` for avatar SVG sub-pixel tolerance\n\n#### Test 2: `State variants › Profile page › transactions tab — empty state` (line 90)\n- **Line Range**: 90–135\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Navigates to `/profile` with wallet disconnected\n  - Connects wallet\n  - Clicks the \"Transactions\" tab\n  - Waits for `.profile-transactions__empty` selector to render\n  - Captures full-page screenshot: `profile-transactions-empty.png`\n  - Uses `maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.03`\n  - Tests the empty state when user has no transaction history\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts`\n\n#### Test: `Route baselines › profile page` (line 39)\n- **Line Range**: 39–42\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Navigates to `/profile`\n  - Captures full-page screenshot: `profile.png`\n  - Basic route baseline (doesn't interact with wallet or tabs)\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Visual Baseline Snapshots**\n\n**Directory**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/`\n\n| Baseline | Test Source | Purpose |\n|----------|-------------|---------|\n| `states.spec.ts/profile-connected.png` | states.spec.ts:51 | Profile page with connected wallet |\n| `states.spec.ts/profile-transactions-empty.png` | states.spec.ts:90 | Transactions tab empty state |\n| `routes.spec.ts/profile.png` | routes.spec.ts:39 | Profile page route baseline |\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Backend Integration Tests**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/__tests__/integration.test.ts`\n\n**Test Suite**: `Integration: create → join → settle lifecycle` (line 243)\n\n#### Test: `full lifecycle: create → join (mock) → settle → verify` (line 311)\n- **Line Range**: 311–488\n- **Coverage**:\n  - End-to-end integration of create match → join → settlement\n  - Exercises the full HTTP middleware stack (JWT auth)\n  - Tests `settleMatch()` which internally calls `db.insertUserTransaction()` for:\n    - JOIN event for creator\n    - WIN/LOSS events for both players\n    - REFUND events if applicable (for closecall)\n  - Verifies on-chain account state matches DB state\n  - Verifies transaction signatures are recorded\n\n#### Additional Tests (lines 489–545):\n- `GET /rounds/:pda returns 404 for unknown PDA` (line 489)\n- `unsettled round does not expose secret` (line 495) — includes transaction writes\n- `two creates from same wallet succeed (different match IDs)` (line 522)\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Backend Database Layer**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts`\n\n#### Function: `insertUserTransaction()` (line 533)\n- **Signature**: `insertUserTransaction(params: InsertUserTransactionParams): Promise<void>`\n- **Line Range**: 533–546\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Inserts rows into `user_transactions` table\n  - Fields: wallet, game, match_id, event, amount_lamports, tx_sig\n  - Uses `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` for idempotency\n  - Target: UNIQUE constraint on (wallet, match_id, event)\n\n#### Function: `getUserTransactions()` (line 548)\n- **Signature**: `getUserTransactions(wallet: string, cursor?: string, limit?: number, game?: string): Promise<UserTransaction[]>`\n- **Line Range**: 548–583\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Fetches paginated transaction history for a wallet (newest first)\n  - Supports optional cursor-based pagination (id-based, DESC order)\n  - Supports optional game filter (coinflip, lord, closecall)\n  - Clamps limit to max 50\n  - Returns normalized UserTransaction objects\n  - Four query branches: (no cursor + no game), (cursor + no game), (no cursor + game), (cursor + game)\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Backend Profile Routes**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/routes/profile.ts`\n\n#### Route: `GET /profile/transactions` (line 34)\n- **Line Range**: 34–89\n- **Coverage**:\n  - Requires JWT authentication (wallet extracted from token)\n  - Query params: `cursor` (pagination), `limit` (1–50, default 20), `game` (filter by game)\n  - Maps game names (both DB format: coinflip/lord/closecall and frontend format: coinflip/lord-of-rngs/close-call)\n  - Calls `db.getUserTransactions()`\n  - Returns array of transactions with fields: id, game, matchId, event, amountLamports, txSig, createdAt\n  - Includes `nextCursor` for pagination\n  - Handles errors with 500 status and logs to logger\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Settlement Transaction Writes**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n\n**Transaction Inserts** (line 307, 315, 520, 532):\n- Called by `settleMatch()` during settlement worker lifecycle\n- Writes one row per user-visible event:\n  - JOIN: when player joins a round\n  - WIN: when player wins\n  - LOSS: when player loses\n  - REFUND: when transaction is reversed (closecall-specific)\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Database Schema**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/migrations/008_user_transactions.sql`\n\n**Table**: `user_transactions` (lines 7–16)\n- Columns: id (BIGSERIAL PK), wallet, game, match_id, event, amount_lamports, tx_sig, created_at\n- Indexes:\n  - `idx_user_tx_wallet_created` on (wallet, created_at DESC) — for paginated history\n  - `idx_user_tx_match_id` on (match_id) — for dedup/lookup\n- Constraint: UNIQUE (wallet, match_id, event) — ensures idempotency\n\n---\n\n### 9. **No Unit Tests Found**\n\n- ❌ No vitest unit tests for `useTransactions` hook\n- ❌ No vitest unit tests for `ProfileTransactions` component\n- ❌ No vitest unit tests for `useSolPrice` hook\n- ⚠️ Component files exist but are not tested in isolation:\n  - `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`\n  - `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts`\n\n---\n\n### Summary Table\n\n| Test Type | Location | Test Name | Line(s) | Scope |\n|-----------|----------|-----------|---------|-------|\n| **Local E2E** | `20-profile-transactions.spec.ts` | shows transaction history after coinflip settlement | 37–116 | Full coinflip lifecycle → profile transactions verification |\n| **Visual Snapshot** | `states.spec.ts` | wallet connected (profile page) | 51–88 | Profile page with connected wallet baseline |\n| **Visual Snapshot** | `states.spec.ts` | transactions tab — empty state | 90–135 | Empty transaction history baseline |\n| **Visual Snapshot** | `routes.spec.ts` | profile page | 39–42 | Profile route 