Maps game names (both DB format: coinflip/lord/closecall and frontend format: coinflip/lord-of-rngs/close-call)\n  - Calls `db.getUserTransactions()`\n  - Returns array of transactions with fields: id, game, matchId, event, amountLamports, txSig, createdAt\n  - Includes `nextCursor` for pagination\n  - Handles errors with 500 status and logs to logger\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Settlement Transaction Writes**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n\n**Transaction Inserts** (line 307, 315, 520, 532):\n- Called by `settleMatch()` during settlement worker lifecycle\n- Writes one row per user-visible event:\n  - JOIN: when player joins a round\n  - WIN: when player wins\n  - LOSS: when player loses\n  - REFUND: when transaction is reversed (closecall-specific)\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Database Schema**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/migrations/008_user_transactions.sql`\n\n**Table**: `user_transactions` (lines 7–16)\n- Columns: id (BIGSERIAL PK), wallet, game, match_id, event, amount_lamports, tx_sig, created_at\n- Indexes:\n  - `idx_user_tx_wallet_created` on (wallet, created_at DESC) — for paginated history\n  - `idx_user_tx_match_id` on (match_id) — for dedup/lookup\n- Constraint: UNIQUE (wallet, match_id, event) — ensures idempotency\n\n---\n\n### 9. **No Unit Tests Found**\n\n- ❌ No vitest unit tests for `useTransactions` hook\n- ❌ No vitest unit tests for `ProfileTransactions` component\n- ❌ No vitest unit tests for `useSolPrice` hook\n- ⚠️ Component files exist but are not tested in isolation:\n  - `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`\n  - `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts`\n\n---\n\n### Summary Table\n\n| Test Type | Location | Test Name | Line(s) | Scope |\n|-----------|----------|-----------|---------|-------|\n| **Local E2E** | `20-profile-transactions.